p=\frac{1}{2}
A\in\mathcal{F}_{n}
\int_{A}E[Y_{n+1}\mid\mathcal{F}_{n}]\, dP=\int_{A}Y_{n+1}\, dP
\int_{A}Y_{n+1}\, dP=0
P[Y_{n+1}=1]=\frac{1}{2}
P[Y_{n+1}=-1]=\frac{1}{2}
p<\frac{1}{2}
\int_{A}\, Y_{n+1}\, dP<0
E[X_{n+1}\mid\mathcal{F}_{n}]<X_{n}
